General.Name: Elon AB (publ)
General.Description: Elon AB (publ) engages in retailing of consumer electronics and telecom products. The company offer concepts and services in trade and logistics to retail chains, e-retailers, and companies in various industries. Elon AB (publ) was formerly known as ELON Group AB. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Orebro, Sweden. Elon AB (publ) operates as a subsidiary of Elon Group Holding Ab (Publ).
